--> Middleware is a kind of function which execute when the node server is started
--> it executes only in sequence manner.
--> (req, res, next) => {} - this is the syntax of custom middleware
    the req & res cycle shoule be done then only the middleware go to next middleware process. the 3rd param 'next' function will 
    close the current middleware and then start executing the next middleware in a sequence manner.

--> TEMPLATE ENGINES
--> it is used to return data with some html structure
--> we use pug lib to create a html template